    <div class="wrap wrap-center wrap-center-narrow">
      <div class="section-spaced">
        <div class="section-summary">
          <div class="section-heading">Open Y Platform</div>
          <p class="section-lead">Open Y is a Drupal 8 CMS platform that gives your YMCA a brand-compliant, modern and mobile responsive website at a fraction of the cost & time of standard web development. It offers key features specifically developed to meet the needs of YMCA's like yours, mobile-friendly responsive themes, content scheduling and management tools, location finder, alerts and integrations with 3rd party services.</p> 
          <p>{{ button.scrollto('openy', 'Sound Good? Lets Talk') }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

  <section class="bg-openy-intro knockout section-right">
    <div class="wrap wrap-center-narrow">
      <div class="section-spaced">
        <div class="section-summary">
          <div class="section-heading">The content management system for YMCA's</div>
          <p>The advantages of an Open Y website are numerous, its open-source and free to use, with no licensing fees, its extendible and customizable, capable of handling any requirement your YMCA has, from multilingual support, sophisticated publishing workflows and microsites. Not to mention there is a huge worldwide community of developers working constantly to keep things up-to-date and secure. </p>
          <p>With the Open Y platform you and your staff can easily administer and manage all aspects of your website’s content and capabilities. Giving you complete control over how and when your content is scheduled, approved and launched.</p>
          <p>If your YMCA needs a powerful website, consider a strategically-built, expertly designed Open Y website.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

