  <section class="integrated">
    <div class="wrap wrap-full wrap-center wrap-center-narrow">
      <div class="section-spaced">
        <div class="section-summary">
          <h1 class="section-heading">Our Open-Y Process</h1>
          <p class="section-lead">The Open Y Platform is a powerful tool and as it can be a challenge to use it to its fullest potential. We'll work with you and help guide you though the process every step of the way from initial planning through training and maintenance.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <ul class="flex-blocks flex-blocks-nowrap">
            <li>
              <div>
                <div class="number">1</div>
                <h3>Understand Your Y and Make a Plan</h3>
                <p>No two Y's are exactly alike. We'll get to know you're particular YMCA, how many locations you have, whether or not you have camps, child services or other special interest sites. We'll help you determine the look and feel of your site and whether or not custom design is somehting you'll need. We'll determine if you're YMCA will need any additional functionality beyond the Open-Y Platform. And lastly we'll decide where the site will be hosted.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div>
                <div class="number">2</div>
                <h3>Content Development</h3>
                <p>We'll work with you to help arrange and organize your content to provide your users with the best possible user experience. We're SEO and content marketing strategists so we can help determine what pages are most important to your users, whether or not you are addressing your audiences needs from awareness through membership and advocacy.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div>
                <div class="number">3</div>
                <h3>Design and Develop</h3>
                <p>We'll install the Open Y Platform and make any theme or template adjustments based on your design requirements. We'll also build and install any custom functionality requirements your particular YMCA might require, such as integration with DAXCO, YWEB or Christianson registration systems.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div>
                <div class="number">4</div>
                <h3>Launch, Monitor and Improve</h3>
                <p>When your ready, we'll help handle all the launch details to ensure a smooth transition from your existing website to your new Open Y site. Your members will not experience any downtime. From here we'll monitor the site, look for ways to help you improve your users experience, keep your site up-to-date and secure with any Drupal security patches.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div>
                <div class="number">5</div>
                <h3>Training and Consultation</h3>
                <p>The open Y Platform is powerful and complex. We make it easy by providing in-person training sessions. So you and your staff with have the opportunity to really get to know and understand the Open Y System. Ask questions and feel confident about using the tool to its fullest potential. Have questions afterwards? No problem we're a phone call or an email away and are alway happy to help you work through a sticky situation or trouble shoot a problem you're having.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

