            <li>Planning, Strategy and Consultation</li>
            <li>Content Strategy, Development or Migrations</li>
            <li>Open Y Platform Installation, Setup &amp; Configuration</li>
            <li>Custom Theme Design and Implementation</li>
            <li>Custom Functionality</li>
            <li>Custom 3rd Party Integrations</li>
            <li>Multi-site, multi-lingual installations</li>
            <li>Secure Hosting and Management</li>
            <li>Security, Web Maintenance &amp; Updates</li>
            <li>Search Engine Optimization</li>
