            <li>In-person Training, Support &amp; Consultation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

  <section class="knockout solutions-openy section-background">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="flex-panels">
        <div class="section-summary flex-panel-6">
          <h2>Let's Talk Open Y!</h2>
          <p>Lets get to know each other! We'll ask you some questions and learn how you see the Open Y Platform fitting into your specific YMCA's needs. We'll give you some ideas, suggestions and recommendations to think about and let you know how we would best be able to help. Lastly we'll see if you'd like to take any next steps forward as you consider an Open Y website. </p>
          <p class="bold">Would that be worth a 1/2 hour of your time?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-panel-6">
          <form>
            <input name="consultation-call" type="hidden" value="{{ about }}">
            <div>
              <label>Name</label>
              <input name="name" placeholder="Full Name" type="text" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label>Company</label>
              <input name="company" placeholder="Company Name" type="text" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label>Email</label>
              <input name="email" placeholder="Email Address" type="email" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label>Phone</label>
              <input name="tel" pattern="[\(]?\d{3}[\)]?[ ]?\d{3}[\-| ]?\d{4}" placeholder="Phone Number (999) 999-9999" type="tel" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <input name="Submit" value="Lets Schedule a Call" type="submit">
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>


